title: Sandra de Lange on Moloto bus and truck accident
description:
Twenty-nine people were killed when a bus collided with a truck on Moloto Road near Kwaggafontein in Mpumalanga on Monday night. 8 people are still in a critical condition in hospital.
For an update on the latest we are joined by assignment editor Sandra de Lange, who is in our Pretoria studio.
